...What do you think you're doing,
coming here uninvited?

rows.label: qst201810_msg0002
rows.name:
This isn't a place for humans.
Hurry up and get lost.

The Vacillus Antol has gone
in the direction of the Ruined Chapel
of Danafas.

rows.label: qst201810_msg0004

Please, I hope you'll take care
of my friends.
